  "text": "Preparation of total RNA and quantification of mRNA expression by qRT-PCR was performed as previously described. Probes used for Taqman qRT-PCR carried 59FAM and 39BHQ1 labels. Sequences of primers and probes spanned exon-intron boundaries: mu-iNOS: 59-CAGCTGGGCTGTACAAACCTT-39, 59-CATTGGA-AGTGAAGCGTTTCG-39, 59-CGGGCAGCCTGTGAGACCTTTGA-39, muHprt: 59-GACCGGTCCCGTCATGC-39, 59-TCATAACCTGGTTCATCATCGC-39, 59-ACCCGCAGTCCCAGCGTCGTC-39 [CITATION_1] .",
